                         <li>
                          Commitment from other research: 
                          </li>
                          
                          <li>
Review process: starts at {{ call_for_proposal.reviewProcessEnd ? call_for_proposal.reviewProcessEnd|date('Y-m-d H:i:s') : '' }}
